data.description: Nestled on a generous 1-acre lot, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort and space. This home includes three spacious bedrooms, two well-appointed bathrooms, including one in the primary suite for added convenience. An inviting living room that serves as the heart of the home, where memories are made, and a cozy family room for relaxation. This home also includes a cozy fireplace nestled in the living room which adds warmth and ambiance to the home, making it an inviting and comfortable space for relaxation. The expansive 1-acre lot is a nature lover's paradise, providing endless opportunities for outdoor activities, gardening, and peaceful strolls. The sparkling blue pool in the backyard offers a refreshing escape on hot summer days, providing a perfect spot for relaxation and enjoyment. This home is ideal setting for those seeking a tranquil lifestyle while still being conveniently close to the conveniences of modern living. NO SUBJECT TO OPTIONS.
